  </div>

  <section class="quick-nav">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#soccer">Soccer</a>
        <a href="#baseball">Baseball & Softball</a>
        <a href="#football">Football</a>
        <a href="#basketball">Basketball</a>
        <a href="#other">Other Sports</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sports-section" id="soccer">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>‚öΩ Soccer</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">All three organizations play in the <strong>Lorain County Soccer League (LCSL)</strong> together. Registration typically opens in fall (for spring) and spring (for fall).</p>

      <div class="programs-grid">
        <div class="program-card">
          <h3>Midview Soccer League</h3>
          <p class="serves">Serves: Grafton, Eaton Twp, Carlisle Twp (Midview area)</p>
