            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:oberlinbaseballsoftball@gmail.com">oberlinbaseballsoftball@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Baseball Contact:</strong> Jodi Cool ‚Äî <a href="tel:440-864-1817">440-864-1817</a></p>
