          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="program-card">
          <h3>Flag Football Fanatics</h3>
          <p class="serves">Lorain area (flag football option)</p>
          <div class="program-details">
            <p><strong>Ages:</strong> 4-14 (PreK/K, 1st-2nd, 3rd-4th divisions)</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://playfanatics.com/programs/west-cleveland-lorain-spring/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">playfanatics.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="note">Cheerleading typically paired with football programs. Check JR LC8 Facebook for cheer squad info.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sports-section alt" id="basketball">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>üèÄ Basketball</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Registration typically in fall (Oct-Nov) for winter season.</p>

      <div class="programs-grid">
        <div class="program-card">
          <h3>Keystone Youth Sports Basketball</h3>
          <p class="serves">Serves: LaGrange, Carlisle Twp (Keystone area)</p>
