            <p><strong>Ages:</strong> K-6th grade</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> K/1st: $15, 2nd/3rd: $30</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://keystoneyouthsports.com/basketball/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">keystoneyouthsports.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:keystoneyouthbasketball@gmail.com">keystoneyouthbasketball@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> Jeff Holzhauer ‚Äî <a href="mailto:jeffrey.holzhauer@keystoneschools.org">jeffrey.holzhauer@keystoneschools.org</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="fields">
            <strong>Gyms:</strong> Keystone Middle School, Saturdays
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="program-card">
          <h3>Midview Youth Basketball</h3>
          <p class="serves">Serves: Grafton, Eaton Twp (Midview area)</p>
          <div class="program-details">
            <p><strong>Ages:</strong> Youth (K-8 feeder programs)</p>
            <p><strong>Registration:</strong> <a href="https://forms.gle/8qRgNnG8Nc2Esqp89" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Interest Form</a></p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://www.midviewathletics.com/youth-sports/youth-sports-programs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Midview Athletics</a></p>
            <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:dmay@midviewk12.org">dmay@midviewk12.org</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="program-card">
          <h3>Oberlin Parks & Rec Youth Basketball</h3>
          <p class="serves">Serves: Oberlin area</p>
          <div class="program-details">
            <p><strong>Ages:</strong> K-2nd grade (beginner/rec)</p>
            <p><strong>Cost:</strong> $30 resident, $40 non-resident</p>
            <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://cityofoberlin.com/city-government/departments/recreation/youth-recreation/youth-basketball/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oberlin Recreation</a></p>
